<h3>Question 5</h3>
<div><p><p>Describe behavior of mobile negative charges in the Hall effect experiment.</p</p></div><div><strong>Answer:</strong><br><style>body .mathjax_wrap{width: 100%;overflow-x: scroll;margin-bottom:10px;}</style><p>Hall Effect</p>
<p>When magnetic field is applied to the current carrying conductor the voltage is developed across the conductor . The direction of voltage is perpendicular to the direction of both magnetic filed and current. This phenomenon is called Hall Effect and voltage developed is called Hall Voltage.</p>
<p><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-16628" src="https://i0.wp.com/hamrocsit.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Screenshot-2023-05-12-150654.png?resize=290%2C207&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="290" height="207"></p>
<p><em>Figure: Hall Effect</em></p>
<p><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-16629" src="https://i0.wp.com/hamrocsit.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Screenshot-2023-05-12-150814.png?resize=621%2C431&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="621" height="431"></p>
<p><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-16630" src="https://i0.wp.com/hamrocsit.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Screenshot-2023-05-12-150827.png?resize=533%2C534&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="533" height="534"></p>
<p><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-16631" src="https://i0.wp.com/hamrocsit.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Screenshot-2023-05-12-150925.png?resize=534%2C509&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="534" height="509"></p>
<p><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-16632" src="https://i0.wp.com/hamrocsit.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Screenshot-2023-05-12-150932.png?resize=596%2C565&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="596" height="565"></p>
<p>Hence , graph pf ‘B’ versus R is straight line passing through origin as shown in figure below by dotted line.</p>
<p><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-16633" src="https://i0.wp.com/hamrocsit.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Screenshot-2023-05-12-151049.png?resize=262%2C189&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="262" height="189"></p>
